---
title: Roast Eggplant Ratatouille Pearl Couscous with Plant-Based Basil Pesto & Parmesan
description: Ratatouille - we love this Mediterranean veggie dish so much, how can we possibly improve it? We think we’ve found a way. Take all those flavour-packed roast veggies and stir them through perfectly cooked pearl couscous in a tomato-based sauce. For an added yum-factor, top with a dollop of pesto and a flourish of Parmesan cheese.
